{
  "name": "WF6 — Feedback Listener (Inbound WhatsApp)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 6: Feedback Listener\n\n**Trigger:** Webhook POST (always active)\n\n**Webhook URL:** Copy from the Webhook node → Production URL\nRegister this URL in:\n- Twilio: Console → Messaging → Sandbox Settings → \"When a message comes in\"\n- Meta: Developer App → WhatsApp → Configuration → Webhook\n\n**Logic:**\n1. Receives inbound WhatsApp message from Twilio or Meta\n2. Extracts sender phone + message body\n3. Finds matching patient in Patients sheet\n4. Classifies response (confirmed / cancelled / help / responded)\n5. Updates patient record\n6. Sends appropriate auto-reply (within 24h session window)\n7. Logs to System_Logs\n\n**Before activating:**\nSet credentials on all Google Sheets nodes and HTTP Request node.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 440
      },
      "id": "66666666-6666-6666-6666-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "path": "feedback-listener",
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "66666666-6666-6666-6666-000000000002",
      "name": "Webhook — Inbound WhatsApp",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [240, 480],
      "webhookId": "feedback-listener-webhook"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Extract and normalise inbound message data\n// Handles both Twilio and Meta Cloud API webhook formats\nconst body = $input.first().json.body || $input.first().json;\n\nlet fromPhone = '';\nlet messageBody = '';\nlet source = 'unknown';\n\n// Twilio format: body.From = 'whatsapp:+919876543210', body.Body = 'text'\nif (body.From && body.Body !== undefined) {\n  source = 'twilio';\n  fromPhone = body.From.replace(/^whatsapp:/i, '').replace(/[\\s\\-().]/g, '');\n  messageBody = String(body.Body || '').trim();\n}\n// Meta Cloud API format: body.entry[0].changes[0].value.messages[0]\nelse if (body.entry && Array.isArray(body.entry)) {\n  source = 'meta';\n  try {\n    const msg = body.entry[0].changes[0].value.messages[0];\n    fromPhone = '+' + msg.from.replace(/^\\+/, '');\n    messageBody = msg.text?.body || '';\n  } catch (e) {\n    // Not a message event (could be status update) — skip\n    return [{ json: { _skip: true, reason: 'Not a message event (Meta webhook ping or status update)', source: 'meta' } }];\n  }\n}\nelse {\n  return [{ json: { _skip: true, reason: 'Unrecognised webhook format', rawBody: JSON.stringify(body).substr(0, 200) } }];\n}\n\nif (!fromPhone || !fromPhone.startsWith('+')) {\n  return [{ json: { _skip: true, reason: 'Could not extract valid phone from webhook', rawFrom: fromPhone } }];\n}\n\n// Classify the message\nconst lowerMsg = messageBody.toLowerCase();\nlet classification = 'responded';\n\nconst confirmedKeywords = ['yes', 'confirm', 'confirmed', 'will come', 'coming', 'ok', 'okay', 'sure', 'yep', 'yup', 'absolutely', 'definitely', \"i'll be there\", 'see you', 'good', 'well'];\nconst cancelledKeywords = ['no', 'cancel', 'cancelled', 'reschedule', \"can't make it\", 'cannot come', 'not coming', 'postpone', 'change date'];\nconst bookKeywords = ['book', 'schedule', 'appointment', 'want to book', 'fix appointment'];\nconst helpKeywords = ['help', 'not well', 'pain', 'emergency', 'urgent', 'need doctor', 'call me', 'okay', 'okay'];\n\nif (helpKeywords.some(k => lowerMsg.includes(k)) && lowerMsg.includes('help') || lowerMsg === 'help') {\n  classification = 'help';\n} else if (bookKeywords.some(k => lowerMsg.includes(k))) {\n  classification = 'book';\n} else if (confirmedKeywords.some(k => lowerMsg.includes(k))) {\n  classification = 'confirmed';\n} else if (cancelledKeywords.some(k => lowerMsg.includes(k))) {\n  classification = 'cancelled';\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    _from_phone: fromPhone,\n    _message_body: messageBody,\n    _classification: classification,\n    _source: source,\n    _received_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  }\n}];"
      },
